# Frontend UX Rules

- Civilian portal must show: Report Crime, Track My Report, Find Station, Emergency SOS.
- Officer dashboard must include: incident queue, dispatch board, patrols, cell occupancy.
- Judge portal must include: warrant inbox, review panel, signature pad.
- Use role-specific layouts: CivilianLayout, OfficerLayout, JudgeLayout.
- All map layers must support toggles: Hotspots, Stations, Roadblocks, Alerts, My Reports.
